  "text": "In this paper, we have thoroughly investigated the exceptional sigma model, whose form we wrote down in [CITATION_1] . This is the action for a string coupled to a background of exceptional field theory, a unified reformulation of the 11-dimensional and type II supergravities. It generalises the doubled sigma model",
